{
  "stem": "17526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 86.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as far-- so far we know, there's very few left from this particular camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was near the Swiss border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was one of the harshest [BACKROUND NOISE] ones that I've been in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said before, good morning-- the good morning call was with two criminal inmates staying on both sides and clubbing us going to the washroom, going out in the morning to work.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the work was torture, absolutely torture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every day, somebody tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember one morning, this guy was-- this inmate, he was sleeping in the bunk right next to me, and somebody stole his cap.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Naturally, everybody stole from everybody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stole his cap so he accused the other guy of stealing the cap, and he fought with the other inmate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So later on in the day, this very same guy was trying to escape, and he was shot and then he was brought back to the camp and he was laid right in the center and everybody had to walk around him.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I says, oh my god, he just-- he just fought with the other guy this morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When they brought him, he was laying naked with bullet wounds right here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we all had to walk around it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't enough how they-- how they tortured us in this camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to look at the guy and we were-- this was a warning, if you try to do it, this is what's going to happen to you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I broke down physically in this camp, and I could not cope with it any longer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I could hardly walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a name for us, Muselmann-- Muselmann, Muselmann was the name.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
